name: Poster Print "Follow Me"
description:
THIS OPTION IS FOR A POSTER PRINT(NOT THE ORIGINAL)

16" x 20" POSTER PRINT

I hold the deep belief that peace is what will save this world. Considering myself to be a new age hippie, I have an affinity for the late ‘60’s, early ‘70’s era. I admire the love and unity that was amongst the people during that time. All too often this country is at war, with its self, and abroad. I am a huge anti-war & humans rights activist, which most definitely has inspired this piece. The woman in the painting is leading the way and if people would simply follow her on the path to peace, all would be healed.
